#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:5
#: 6e734e05a72b4c2d84009793a132885a
msgid "The European Fishing Control Agency's `Guidelines on Risk Assessment Methodology <https://www.efca.europa.eu/en/content/guidelines-risk-assessment-methodology-fisheries-compliance>`_ define fleet segments as *'fishery units with similar fishing characteristics (e.g., gear, area and target species)'*."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:9
#: 26eb64d102c244739544fb1226c6506c
msgid "Each member state is responsible for defining the fleet segments relevant to its waters and to perform risk assessments on each segment."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:15
#: e1fc906b904b4752b1be747ea2c55472
msgid "Fleet segment risk assessment and control objectives"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:17
#: cf94a50ef5054ff0b907102e5a8dc71e
msgid "In France, fleet segments were defined by the `Direction des Pêches Maritimes et de l'Aquaculture <https://agriculture.gouv.fr/administration-centrale>`_, and risk assessments on these fleet segments are performed each year by the `Directions Interrégionales de la Mer <https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Direction_interr%C3%A9gionale_de_la_Mer#:~:text=Les%20directions%20interr%C3%A9gionales%20de%20la,marin%20et%20gestion%20des%20ressources>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:21
#: 56de45a5ce9642ac9312edb93aa3b177
msgid "During this process, a risk level is computed for each fleet segment based on"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:23
#: d80e6f55a26e4a04b18ebd8eb865ef9b
msgid "scientific data on the **state of the stock** (healthy, threatened, collapsed...)"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:24
#: 56933166321c4a2fad3ed46eece7dda9
msgid "national metrics to estimate the pressure that the fishing activity puts on the stock and the level of non-compliance observed on the fleet segment"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:26
#: 5b5d2483629b4bb2a17324d600419451
msgid "In addition, and based on the risk assessment conclusions, an objective of a minimum number of controls to perform on each fleet segment is defined."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/fleet-segments.rst:29
